---
import CtaButton from "./CtaButton.astro";
import SatisfiedCounter from "./SatisfiedCounter.astro";
---

<section class="bg-[#0e0e0e] px-[5%] py-12 md:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
    <p class="mb-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#777]">
      BE HONEST WITH YOURSELF
    </p>
    <h2 class="mb-6 font-heading text-2xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-heading text-[#fff] md:text-4xl">
      30 days from now, two things will happen.
    </h2>

    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#999]">
      Either you'll still be guessing at creatives, burning budget, and wondering why nothing scales...
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#999]">
      Or you'll have
      <span class="font-semibold text-cta-yellow">
        a swipe file of 500+ winning supplement ads, AI workflows generating creatives on demand, and a ROAS that actually makes your ad spend worth it.
      </span>
    </p>
    <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#999]">
      Same 30 days either way. The only difference is the decision you make right now.
    </p>

    <CtaButton variant="yellow" />
    <SatisfiedCounter variant="dark" />
  </div>
</section>
